post.description:
Adds a new notification template.  

The following is an example of the request body parameter **templateConfig** for a request 
to add an email notification template. This configuration requests an email notification 
template that has both a custom note and a custom link.

```json
{
  "enabled": true,
  "templateConfig": {
    "basic_config": [
      {
        "displayName": "Custom Note",
        "fieldName": "custom_note",
        "options": [],
        "type": "text",
        "value": ""
      }
    ],
    "dismissed": [],
    "open": [],
    "resolved": []
  },
  "integrationType": "email",
  "templateType": "ticketing",
  "name": "template name"
}
```

